description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=1/3, Sex=0/3, Mature Content=1/3. The space mercenaries are back and are ready for new missions. Play as Star, Trey, and Lain along with new characters. Choose between a variety of missions and change your squad. StarWings is a side view shoot'em up game.
